**Part 2: Impact Summary (4-Row Matrix)**

🚨 Dynamically calculate based on items above.

| Strategy Bucket | Net Budget Impact | Est. Conversion Lift | Efficiency Note |
|-----------------|-------------------|---------------------|-----------------|
| 🛡️ Defense | +${Total_Savings} Saved | 0 | Removes {X}% Wasted Spend |
| ⚔️ Offense | -${Total_Investment} Invested | +{X} Conv. | Scales Proven Winners |
| 🔧 Tactics | $0 | +{X} Conv. | Improves Quality Score |
| 🚀 **TOTAL** | **±${Net} Net Saved** | **+{Total} Monthly Conv.** | CPA Drops ~{X}% |

**Calculation:**
- Offense Conv.: Total Investment / Target CPA
- Tactics Conv.: +5% from Quality Score improvement
- Total: (Defense Savings - Offense Investment)

